<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Logo Implementation Guide</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .code-block {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #1976d2;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Logo Implementation Guide</h1>
  
  <h2>1. Save the SVG file</h2>
  <p>First, save the provided SVG code as "logo-source.svg"</p>
  
  <h2>2. Generate PNG files</h2>
  <p>Use the SVG to generate the required PNG files at the specified dimensions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>logo.png - 512x512 pixels</li>
    <li>logo192.png - 192x192 pixels</li>
    <li>logo512.png - 512x512 pixels</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can use tools like Inkscape, Adobe Illustrator, or online converters to generate these PNGs from the SVG.</p>
  
  <h2>3. Generate favicon.ico</h2>
  <p>Create the favicon.ico file containing multiple sizes (16x16, 24x24, 32x32, and 64x64). You can use online favicon generators like:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://realfavicongenerator.net/">RealFaviconGenerator</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.favicon-generator.org/">Favicon Generator</a></li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>4. Update your HTML</h2>
  <div class="code-block">
  <pre><code>&lt;!-- Basic favicon -->
&lt;link rel="icon" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/favicon.ico" />

&lt;!-- iOS icon -->
&lt;link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/logo192.png" />

&lt;!-- Add to manifest.json -->
&lt;!-- Make sure your manifest.json includes the logo references: -->
</code></pre>
  </div>
  
  <h2>5. Example manifest.json</h2>
  <div class="code-block">
  <pre><code>{
  "short_name": "Coupon App",
  "name": "Coupon Discount App",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "favicon.ico",
      "sizes": "64x64 32x32 24x24 16x16",
      "type": "image/x-icon"
    },
    {
      "src": "logo192.png",
      "type": "image/png",
      "sizes": "192x192"
    },
    {
      "src": "logo512.png",
      "type": "image/png",
      "sizes": "512x512"
    }
  ],
  "start_url": ".",
  "display": "standalone",
  "theme_color": "#1976d2",
  "background_color": "#ffffff"
}</code></pre>
  </div>
</body>
</html>